### User Management API Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###############################################
# Available Endpoints:
# 1. Login - Get JWT token
# 2. GET All Users (paginated)
# 3. GET Active Users (dedicated endpoint)
# 4. GET Inactive Users (dedicated endpoint)
# 5-7. GET Users - With various filters
# 8. GET Single User
# 9. POST Create User
# 10. PUT Update User
# 11. DELETE Soft Delete (via DELETE method)
# 12. POST Reactivate User
# 13. PATCH Change User Status (Activate/Deactivate)
# 14. GET User Status History
###############################################

### 1. Login as Admin (to get access token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@domain.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 2. Get All Users (Active and Inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch?PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Get All Active Users (Dedicated Endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch/true?PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Get All Inactive Users (Dedicated Endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch/false?PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Get All Active Users (Using Query Parameter - Alternative)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch?IsActive=true&PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Get All Inactive Users (Using Query Parameter - Alternative)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch?IsActive=false&PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Get Users by Role (e.g., Employee)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch?Role=Employee&PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Get Users by Department
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/fetch?Department=Sales&PageNumber=1&PageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Get Specific User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10. Create New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/create
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Williams",
  "email": "alice.williams@domain.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+27123456789",
  "password": "Alice123!",
  "role": "Employee",
  "department": "Marketing",
  "employeeNumber": "EMP006",
  "primaryLocation": "London",
  "preferredLocation": "London",
  "notificationPreferences": "Email"
}

### 11. Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/update
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@domain.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+27987654321",
  "department": "Sales",
  "primaryLocation": "CapeTown",
  "notificationPreferences": "Both"
}

### 12. Soft Delete User (Mark as Inactive)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Employee resigned"
}

### 13. Reactivate Soft-Deleted User
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/reactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14. Change User Active Status (Activate or Deactivate)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "isActive": true,
  "reason": "Employee returned from leave"
}

### 14b. Deactivate User (Alternative to DELETE)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "isActive": false,
  "reason": "Employee on long-term leave"
}

### 15. Get User Status Change History
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/USER_ID_HERE/history
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 16. Get All Status Changes (All Users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserManagement/history/all?pageNumber=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### RoomLocation Values (use string names)
# - London
# - CapeTown
# - Johannesburg
# - Bloemfontein
# - Durban

### Available Roles
# - Admin
# - FacilityManager
# - Receptionist
# - Employee

### NotificationPreferences Options
# - Email
# - SMS
# - Both
# - None
